quran[33]{c,v,t,f}:
  74,49,"Ee maxaa heysta iyaga oo ay uga jeestaan (qaadashada) waanada?"
  74,50,"Sida inay yihiin dameero duur joog ah oo didsan."
  74,51,"Ee ka soo cararay libaax?"
  77,37,"Hoog Maalintaas waxaa leh xaq beeniyayaasha (nabad diidka)."
  77,38,"Kani waa Maalinka kala Baxa. Waa idin soo kulminnay idinka iyo kuwii horreeyey."
  77,39,"Ee haddaad wax dhagri kartaan, Aniga I dhagra."
  78,34,"Iyo galaas buuxa (oo khamri saafi ah)."
  78,35,"Kuma maqlayaan (Jannada) gudaheeda hadal macno darro ah ama wax been ah."
  78,36,"Abaal marin xagga Rabbigaa; deeq (daa'in ah badan) oo ku filan."
  79,28,"Wuxuu (samada) kor yeelay jurmigeeda oo waliba simay."
  79,29,"Oo ka yeelay mugdi habeenkeeda oo soo bixiyey maalinteeda (ifiyey)."
  79,30,"Dhulka markaa kaddib fidshay."
  80,25,"Annagaa soo shubna biyaha (roobka) soo shubid badan,"
  80,26,"Markaas Waxaan jeexnaa arlada jeexdin."
  80,27,"Oo ka soo bixinnaa hadhuudh,"
  81,22,"Saaxiibkiin (Nabi Muxammad) ma aha jinnoole."
  81,23,"Horay buuna ugu arkay (Jabriil) jihada cad (dhinaca qorrax soo baxa)."
  81,24,"Ma aha (Nabi Muxammad) mid ceshada cilmiga ku saabsan Ghaybka."
  82,16,"Kamana maqnaadaan marnaba xaggeeda (Naarta)."
  82,17,"Maxaa ku ogeysiiyey waxay Maalinta is abaal marintu tahay?"
  82,18,"Misna, maxaa ku ogeysiiyey waxay Maalinta is abaal marintu tahay?"
  83,13,"Marka Aayadahayaga loo akhriyo, yidhaahda: Waa sheekooyinkii dadkii hore."
  83,14,"Mayee’ bal waxay fali jireen (oo macaasi ah) baa waxay ku noqdeen sida mirir madow quluubtooda dushood."
  83,15,"Mayee, hubaal waxaa maalintaa laga xijaabi Rabbigood."
  84,10,"Kanse laga siiyo Kitaabkiisa dhabarkiisa gadaashiisa,"
  84,11,"Wuxuu u yeedhan hoog iyo ba'."
  84,12,"Oo geli naar ololeysa oo hur badan."
  85,7,"Waxay ka ahaayeen goob joog waxay ku falayeen (oo gardarro ah) Mu’miniinta."
  85,8,"Kuma ay qoonsan wax kale aan aheyn inay rumeeyeen Allaah, Adkaadaha Sharafta leh, Ammaanan."
  85,9,"Ee iska leh Mulkiga (iyo Maamulka) samooyinka iyo arlada! Alle wax walba waa u Jeedaa."
  86,1,"Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay samada iyo Xiddigga guura."
  86,2,"Maxaa ku ogeysiiyey waxa uu xiddiga guura) yahay?"
  86,3,"Waa xiddiggaa iftiinka badan."
